TUX PICROSS

Manual Installation
-------------------

Configure the path to the gfx directory by setting FILEPREFIX 
in f_sdlfrontend.h. By default, FILEPREFIX is configured to 
load from ./gfx.

Examples for other configurations:

//loads from ../gfx
#define FILEPREFIX "../"

//loads from /usr/share/tuxpicross/gfx
#define FILEPREFIX "/usr/share/tuxpicross/"

To install, enter the src directory and run 

make

Installation from AUR (Archlinux)
-------------------

Package Name: tuxpicross
URL: http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=35212


Enjoy!